Multivariate standard normal data

Source: R/datasets.R
n01.Rd

A synthetic data set containing 1000 observations on 10 variables generated from independent standard normal distributions.

Usage

n01

Format

A data frame with 1000 rows and 10 columns.

Value

Data frame

Examples

n01
